            "processed": "<p>Founded in 2010, Lumiere Photography has grown from a one-person passion project into a full-service photography studio serving clients across the Pacific Northwest and beyond.</p><h2>Our Philosophy</h2><p>We believe every photograph should tell a story. Our approach combines technical precision with artistic vision, creating images that are both beautiful and meaningful. The name \"Lumiere\" -- French for light -- reflects our dedication to mastering the interplay of light and shadow that makes photography an art form.</p><h2>Our Team</h2><p>Our team of five photographers brings diverse specialties and perspectives, ensuring we can match the right artist to every project. From intimate portrait sessions to large-scale commercial shoots, we approach every assignment with creativity and professionalism.</p><h2>Awards & Recognition</h2><ul><li>International Photography Awards - Gold, Wedding Category (2024)</li><li>Professional Photographers of America - Master Photographer designation</li><li>Best of Portland - Top Photography Studio (2022-2025)</li></ul>",
